l a gap on replay         - PK2: (caller,seqNum): Allows a tx search to audit a sequence for a caller     - Context: `replay` and `callRes.blockNum` provide context on when/where this happened     - Output: `callRes` provides fields (rc, lrc, count) for either a simple result or summary         - Additional results can be found in the tx receipt logs from prior events in the same tx\",\"params\":{\"callRes\":\"See `CallRes`; `reqId` and `ReqAck` are separate params for indexes\",\"caller\":\"Account initiating the tx\",\"replay\":\"false for an original event, true when `reqId` was already processed\",\"reqId\":\"From CallRes: Request ID, allows for gap-fill on replay\",\"seqNum\":\"From CallRes: Caller's sequence number incremented monotonically\"}}},\"kind\":\"dev\",\"methods\":{},\"version\":1},\"userdoc\":{\"kind\":\"user\",\"methods\":{},\"version\":1}},\"settings\":{\"compilationTarget\":{\"contract/v1_0/IBalanceMgr.sol\":\"IBalanceMgr\"},\"evmVersion\":\"prague\",\"libraries\":{},\"metadata\":{\"bytecodeHash\":\"ipfs\"},\"optimizer\":{\"enabled\":true,\"runs\":200},\"remappings\":[\":@openzeppelin/contracts-upgradeable/=lib/openzeppelin-contracts-upgradeable/contracts/\",\":@openzeppelin/contracts/=lib/openzeppelin-contracts/contracts/\",\":forge-std/=lib/forge-std/src/\",\":openzeppelin-contracts-upgradeable/=lib/openzeppelin-contracts-upgradeable/\",\":openzeppelin-contracts/=lib/openzeppelin-contracts/\"],\"viaIR\":true},\"sources\":{\"contract/v1_0/IBalanceMgr.sol\":{\"keccak256\":\"0x9e955b1f577d05f65f4e93a2aaa9c165811074cee2b3caf1489a46930d0f76f5\",\"license\":\"UNLICENSED\",\"urls\":[\"bzz-raw://2e04f026d2e7abcf36d2bf322990a5d495d84acc3935288502d6362fded30536\",\"dweb:/ipfs/QmaL73F4qTeUfhHNWGxm1LA8KUUj9Vkcb317AnUovM3iAD\"]},\"contract/v1_0/ICallTracker.sol\":{\"keccak256\":\"0x55771cf0eb77cd29635e23a90dfc280d8b0554cb41c381a93421b68a5deee866\",\"license\":\"UNLICENSED\",\"urls\":[\"bzz-raw://b0054d759dd7137160a26d220a87be80bf49a2671d965e3b08784ac71147a6